text: Gan, Pyrénées-Atlantiques is a commune of the Pyrénées-Atlantiques département in the southwestern part of France. Its mayor has been Mr Francis Pèes (Right Wing ; also Vice President of the Communauté d'agglomération de Pau-Pyrénées) since 2014, a former CEO of a construction company. Gan, Pyrénées-Atlantiques
